It has been reported that Nigerian male Barbie and Snapchat queen, Idris Okuneye, most popularly known as Bobrisky, was on Monday arrested by the police over the sum of N665k he owed to a boutique. Since his arrest, there have been many speculations as to why he was arrested, but according to an eyewitness, the arrest was due to the fact that he breached an endorsement agreement between the two parties. Since his arrest, there have been many speculations as to why he was arrested, but according to an eyewitness, the arrest was due to the fact that he breached an endorsement agreement between the two parties. He was, however, later granted bail after signing an undertaking to pay N300k, today, and balance up later. Source